
Kubernetes/K8s

It is a container management platform.

Useful links to learn Kubernetes:
Kubernetes documentation: https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/overview/what-is-kubernetes/
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l_lWfipUimk -> explained very well

use/install K8s
---------------

1. online kubernetes playground

https://www.katacoda.com/courses/kubernetes/playground

https://labs.play-with-k8s.com/

https://training.play-with-kubernetes.com/

2. installation tools

 i) Minikube (quick and easy - if we want to try kubernetes in your local it is good choice)
 
	https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/tools/install-minikube/
	
  ii) Kubeadm
  
	https://kubernetes.io/fr/docs/setup/independent/install-kubeadm/
	
3. cloud based kubernetes services

  GKE - Google Kubernetes Engine
  
  AKS - Azure Kubernetes Service
  
  Amazon EKS
  
  
  Commands reference doc:
  -----------------------
  https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/generated/kubectl/kubectl-commands
  
